title: Locksmith V3
description:
The Locksmith - Lock Picking CD
--------------------------------
Learn the MOST effective Lock Picking techniques used by Locksmiths! "The Locksmith" CD Rom has over 45 minutes of interactive video clips. Easy to follow step by step video that will show you how to pick almost any type of lock. The clips will take you from very basic techniques through advanced techniques. Secret lock picking techniques that you can use in a pinch- learn how to transform ordinary household items like paper clips or safety pins into powerful lock picking tools.
http://www.lockpickshop.com/LPCD.html
